parameter (unit %run);
storage address;
# Records the SENDER of the current call into storage.
#
# Used in CRAC address-identity tests to observe the Michelson-side SENDER
# after a cross-runtime hop (EVM→TEZ CRAC) and in journal-revert tests.
#
# The %run entrypoint is required for compatibility with:
#   - EvmCrossRuntimeRunnerTez (calls gateway callMichelson(dest, "run", ...))
#   - TezMultiRunCaller (calls callee.%run)
#
# Storage is a single `address` initialised to any placeholder (e.g. the gateway
# address).  Each call replaces it with SENDER.
code { DROP; SENDER; NIL operation; PAIR };
